title: Ep 59: Earn More doing Less Honey!
description:
Today's proceedings:  We hear about the most recent Judgies Taco Bell experience. We also have a boyfriend with dog water for brains, an oblivious boyfriend thinks his girlfriend has an eat disorder, another boyfriend who has their priorities straight, and a listener submitted a story about Spartan kicking a bigot into a lake. And for this weeks Circle Jurdge we try to help diagnose Christian after tiktok tried to gaslight him into believing he has a few aliments.
